Usage: ./license-updater directory filetype newlicense [--dry] [--add]
WARNING: Backup your project first and check your source code after running this script

example: ./license-updater /home/user/project *.php license.txt
option --dry: do not actually write to any files
option --add: add license where it is not found

This will replace all FIRST occurences of "/* LICENSE-TEXT */" in every file of your project directory
